    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<h2>How Explainer Videos Simplify Complex Products</h2>
<p>Brands simplify complex products by turning technical details into clear, visual stories through <a href={p("services/how-to-video")}>explainer videos</a>, which break down features step by step and answer common customer questions before they become barriers to purchase. This is especially valuable in industries like technology, finance and healthcare, where Viven specializes in creating explainer videos that simplify complexity while delivering clarity.</p>
<h2>The Value of Explainer Videos</h2>
<p>According to HubSpot, explainer videos increase the understanding of a product by 74%. They are one of the most effective tools for educating potential customers, answering questions and reducing barriers to purchase.</p>
<h2>Viven's Expertise in Explainer Video Production</h2>
<p>Viven's creative team works closely with clients to understand their products and develop scripts and visuals that simplify messaging without losing key details. The result is engaging, informative videos that build trust and drive conversions.</p>
<h3>Explainer Video Services Offered</h3>
<ul>
<li>Animated 2D and 3D videos</li>
<li>Live-action explainer videos</li>
<li>Product walkthroughs</li>
<li>Tutorial and how-to videos</li>
</ul>
<h2>Case Study: Kyan Health — Making Mental Well-Being a Superpower at Work</h2>
<p>Kyan Health, a provider of a healthcare app, partnered with ON to address employee well-being by offering resources like mindfulness meditations, cognitive behavioral exercises and coaching programs, promoting self-care, mental health and work-life balance within the organization.</p>
<p>Kyan Health approached Viven to produce a testimonial video showcasing the app's effectiveness within ON, creating a concise internal version for ON's employees and a second version for external distribution to broaden Kyan Health's reach. Viven handled technical execution during production, ensuring seamless integration of footage, animations and music in post-production. The result was a compelling, natural and engaging video that highlighted the app's benefits and promoted a culture of innovation at ON.</p>
<h2>Why Choose Viven</h2>
<ul>
<li>Deep understanding of complex industries</li>
<li>Simplified messaging without sacrificing key information</li>
<li>High-quality visuals that maintain viewer interest</li>
</ul>
<p>The right explainer video does more than describe a product — it anticipates the questions a prospect would otherwise ask a salesperson, which is exactly why it shortens the path from interest to decision. That's especially true for technical or regulated products, where a short video can pre-empt confusion that would otherwise show up as support tickets or stalled deals later on.</p>
<p>Explainer videos work especially well alongside <a href={p("services/product-video")}>product videos</a> that showcase the finished experience once the concept is understood. For more on how brands use video to reduce sales friction, see <a href={p("blog/the-competitive-advantage-product-video-production-gives")}>The Competitive Advantage Product Video Production Gives</a> and <a href={p("blog/how-big-brands-can-use-video-production-to-promote-customer-events-and-maximize-engagement")}>How Big Brands Can Use Video Production to Promote Customer Events and Maximize Engagement</a>.</p>
<p>👉 <a href={p("contact")}>Simplify your products with Viven explainer videos</a></p>
